Modem control lines

TIOCMGET    Command to get status of modem control bits
TIOCMSET    Command to set status of modem control bits
TIOCMBIC    Command to clear modem control line bits
TIOCMBIS    Command to set modem control line bits

TIOCM_CTS   CTS modem control line bit
TIOCM_RTS   RTS modem control line bit
TIOCM_DSR   DSR modem control line bit
TIOCM_RI    RI modem control line bit
TIOCM_CAR   DCD modem control line bit
